      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://museumsdatabase.com/museums/view/19286"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Every year the society hosts a Harvest Festival and a summer concert series that draw locals and visitors alike.",
